author: Screen Junkies
description:
Marvel's First Family is taking their first steps soon – and we're taking an honest look at the full-length trailer Marvel finally blessed us with! Does this wash the taste of the multiverse saga out of your mouth? Or is it the same slop different decade? Not like anyone reads these descriptions but, yes there will still be a full-blown Honest Trailer this Tuesday for another big ol' wad of Marvel IP. Open wide!
